sub_title: Lawyer at Antis Triantafyllides & Sons LLC
summary:
A highly motivated post-graduated law student at the University of Leiden who aspires to succeed in the legal sphere.  Law is a subject that I truly enjoy and fulfils my dreams.European Union and more specifically European migration law is the area that fascinates me mostly.   

I believe that in order to achieve any goal that you have in your life, it is essential to work hard and I always attempt to face any obstacles with a positive attitude in order to achieve my goals. I am confident that my diverse background, in relation to my experiences acquired through extra-curricular activities and work experience, has contributed to the development of my current skills.
